description: Removes metadata tags from an Amazon RDS resource. For an overview on tagging an Amazon RDS resource, see Tagging Amazon RDS Resources in the Amazon RDS User Guide or Tagging Amazon Aurora and Amazon RDS Resources in the Amazon Aurora User Guide.

parameters.name: ResourceName
parameters.description: The Amazon RDS resource that the tags are removed from. This value is an Amazon Resource Name (ARN). For information about creating an ARN, see Constructing an ARN for Amazon RDS in the Amazon RDS User Guide.

parameters.name: TagKeys
parameters.description: The tag key (name) of the tag to be removed. (string) ---
